9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"p-8 space-y-6\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-lg font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">AI를 &#x27;지시하는 방법&#x27;을 배우세요.</p><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">코드 한 줄 몰라도 상상을 현실로 만드는 비결,<br/>바이브 코딩 오프라인 특강에서 공개합니다.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-between\"><div><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\">한정 기간 혜택</p><p class=\"text-xl font-black text-primary\">특가 129,000원</p></div><a class=\"bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-black text-sm shadow-lg shadow-primary/25 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all\" href=\"/special-lecture\">상세보기</a></div><button class=\"w-full py-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 transition-colors\">다음에 볼게요</button></div><button class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 p-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-full text-white transition-colors z-20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></button></div></div><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 py-20 lg:py-32 border-b border-border\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full pointer-events-none overflow-hidden opacity-30\"><div class=\"absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-primary/20 blur-[120px] rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-indigo-500/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16\